{"tid":1490074,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今次狗打老人絕對係令屋企人改變諗法嘅好機會","createTime":"2019-08-20T04:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T16:12:40.000Z","uid":43420,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"27e064885036722da797063e8380c6384f65bedf","tid":1490074,"uid":43420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:22:22.000Z","msg":"在於藍絲，要完全改變佢地嘅變法只有佢地一直擁護嘅政權，狠狠咁摑佢地一巴。<br />\n<br />\n而今次事件絕對有令佢地對警隊失去信心，甚至有轉向嘅影響力！<br />\n<br />\n建議做法:<br />\n<br />\n我地除左要Spread嘅條片比屋企人，更加要講比佢聽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&rdquo;我地本黎都覺得警察執法無問題，但估唔倒警察會濫用私刑，仲要對老人家&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個方法係佢地諗野角度出發之餘，更會令佢反思警犬咁做係咪做錯。<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，我絕對相信大家都好想自己屋企人蘇醒，希望和理非可以用另類方法去幫大家。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052f6fca4b430166bd560a8b7c991c5533507576","tid":1490074,"uid":43420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9619e3a3ba7d5b45224d46a96c56807977cfec","tid":1490074,"uid":302739,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:27:12.000Z","msg":"藍絲/5毛一定話做戲 佢哋冇得救"},{"pid":"df611aca41b8c68a7cde8b64010494e5cd7a7b61","tid":1490074,"uid":43420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f9619e3a3ba7d5b45224d46a96c56807977cfec","tid":1490074,"uid":302739,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:27:12.000Z","msg":"藍絲/5毛一定話做戲 佢哋冇得救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:28:12.000Z","msg":"多個自己友好過多個敵人，做得幾多得幾多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54f30174d8bea9c4ea3ee514efe55999b7de2dd","tid":1490074,"uid":33437,"lik